---
title: Italian Sausage Tomato Risotto with Tuscan Pork Sausage and Fennel Seeds
description: Risotto is a speciality of Northern Italy where they grow rice instead of wheat that becomes pasta in the South. It's traditionally served in small portions as a 'primo' - a first course before the main. But when something is this delicious why restrict it to a starter?
